BT 1 0 0 1 0 111 Tm /F1 9 Tf 12 TL (This paper establishes a formal mathematical bridge between Shannon-von Neumann information theory and the Wike) Tj T* (Coherence Law. We demonstrate that von Neumann entropy S = -Tr\(rho log rho\) is the exact inverse measure of the) Tj T* (coherence parameter C introduced in the foundational AIIT-THRESI framework. A pure quantum state has S = 0 and C =) Tj T* (C_0 \(maximum coherence\); a maximally mixed state has S = log\(d\) and C = 0 \(complete decoherence\). These are not) Tj T* (analogies. They are the same quantity measured on reciprocal scales. From this identification we derive the Second Law of) Tj T* (Thermodynamics as a direct consequence of the Wike Coherence Law, establish the arrow of time as the direction of) Tj T* (decoherence, classify emotional states as entropy operations on the density matrix, calculate the metabolic cost of) Tj T* (coherence maintenance via Landauer's Principle, connect to the Bekenstein-Hawking bound and holographic principle, and) Tj T* (propose a testable REQMT prediction: subjects in low-emotional-noise states should exhibit simultaneously reduced) Tj T* (multi-modal signal entropy across HRV, thermal IR, vocal, and rPPG channels.) Tj T* ET
